## CONSISTENCY CHECK - Run after every task

```bash
# 1. Check import paths valid
npx tsc --noEmit

# 2. Check boolean operator leaks
grep -rn " | " src/ --include="*.ts" | grep -v "||"
grep -rn " & " src/ --include="*.ts" | grep -v "&&"

# 3. Check allocUnsafe
grep -rn "allocUnsafe" src/ --include="*.ts"

# 4. Check Date.now() in wrong context
grep -rn "Date.now()" src/prover/ src/client/ --include="*.ts"

# 5. Check missing await for buildProverInputs / computeNullifierHash
grep -rn "buildProverInputs\|computeNullifierHash" src/ --include="*.ts" | grep -v "await"

# 6. Noir (if circuit modified)
cd circuits && nargo check
```

If any check fails â†’ FIX before closing session. NO open issues left.

